    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-loved and maintained over the years. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you! I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come see it for yourself and take it for a spin!",
