    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement. The 6-speed manual transmission shifts smoothly, paired with a limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. Performance is enhanced by a refined suspension setup with Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis handles with the precision expected of an M-car. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear acceleration and an intoxicating induction note. A turn-key driver's car for the purist.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Runs well. Interior is clean. All maintenance is current. Serious inquiries only.",
      "price": 34500.0,
