    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in wonderful shape, running smooth and looking great. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you right away! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32000.0,
