    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential analog driver\u2019s car. At its heart is the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is paired with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh to ensure structural and rotational integrity. The chassis dynamics are maintained through a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, offering precise turn-in and high-speed stability. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust and the exhaust note remains crisp. A well-sorted example for the discerning enthusiast.",
